The Software may be deployed within infrastructure owned or controlled by the organization, including environments hosted in public or private cloud providers, provided that the deployment is operated solely for the organization’s internal business use.

This license permits use of the Software only as part of a specific application or system operated by the organization and does not grant rights to reuse the Software as a general-purpose platform across multiple independent software projects or for use by multiple unrelated client organizations.

