### Container Image Redistribution

Licensees may not publish, distribute, or make available container images containing the Software through any public or private container registry, repository, or distribution channel other than those authorized by CogniWorks Pvt. Ltd.

This restriction applies regardless of whether the Software is modified, repackaged, or included as part of another container image.

